    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2013-02-14</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2013-03-11T19:13:07Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Lyon County Economic Development and Conservation Act - Directs the Secretary of the Interior to convey to the city of Yerington, Nevada, identified federal land in Lyon and Mineral Counties.</p> <p>Designates identified federal land in Nevada managed by the Forest Service, to be known as the Wovoka Wilderness, as wilderness and as a component of the National Wilderness Preservation System. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Lyon County Economic Development and Conservation Act</title>
